name: Equality Necklace
description:
You don't have to be gay to have pride! 

Display your support for equality with this necklace and pendant combo. The pendant consists of a hand-stamped metal ring which reads "equality". The metal ring surrounds circle of small glass beads in rainbow colors. Pendant hangs from a 18" chain. Each pendant is created individually by hand which results in each piece being 100% unique.

Chain length can be adjusted. If so desired, please specify in your order.
